title: Available Classic Wayzata Rambler
map_address: Byrondale Ave N near Centeral Ave
posting_body: ['Location!', 'Great opportunity to live in a Classic Mid Century Rambler in the heart of the Big Woods of Wayzata on a large lot.', '4 Bed 3 Bath with 2 separate living spaces.', 'The circular tree lined drive with stone and Hosta welcome you home to this classic rambler.', 'Move in ready, freshly painted , 4 Bedroom 3 bath home features hardwood floors throughout.', 'One level living.', 'Inviting main floor living area with large light filled windows, fully appointed cherry kitchen with granite, pantry and laundry.', 'The adjacent dining area leads to the over-sized private deck and screen gazebo for entertaining.', 'A generous Owners’ suite with 1/2 bath, and 2 additional bedrooms and full bath complete the main level.', 'The front walk out Lower Level provides a second full living space.', 'New carpet and freshly painted Large living area, Full kitchen, laundry, and 3/4 bath, one generous size bedroom and a den/ office.', 'Extremely Large 3-4 car detached garage with ample storage.', '1 garage door is extra tall for Toy / RV parking.', 'The double door is tandem 3 car with large storage room.', 'The lot is huge, private fenced back yard, with large trees, deck, and screened gazebo.', 'Convenient walking access to downtown Wayzata, shops, restaurants, parks and lake Minnetonka.', 'Award winning Wayzata schools.', 'Pets OK (Must be under 25lbs)', 'No Smoking Property', 'Owner prefers 1-2 year lease.', '$3950 Deposit', 'Owner pays for city water, trash, and recycling', 'Tenant responsible for electric, gas, cable/ internet, lawn and snow removal.', 'Please reply to this post to arrange showing.']
